    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #5D3FD3;
            --accent-color: #FFD700;
            --bg: #F9F9F9;
            --text: #1A1A1A;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --radius: 12px;
            --transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        section h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        ul li::before {
            content: "✨";
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Tabs */
        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            background-color: #eee;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .tab-btn.active {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #1A1A1A;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }

        .header-image {
            width: 450px;
            height: auto;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header-image {
                width: 300px;
                height: auto;
            }

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Hero Section -->

    <header>
        <img class="header-image" src="\images\event-logo.png" alt="Mtv Apps">
        <h1>Bring Safety, Joy & Community to Your Event</h1>
        <p>The Magic Code turns lost items into moments of human connection — and gives your guests a meaningful gift
            from partners like MediaMarkt.</p>
        <a href="#request" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
    </header>

    <!-- What is Magic Code? -->
    <section>
        <h2>What is the Magic Code?</h2>
        <p>The Magic Code is a smart sticker powered by auto-ID technology. When guests attach it to their phone,
            wallet, or bag, they instantly gain access to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Instant, anonymous item return if something is lost</li>
            <li>Discreet emergency messaging in urgent situations</li>
            <li>Anonymous peer-to-peer communication between attendees</li>
        </ul>
        <p>And best of all? Each guest receives **3 free stickers** as a gift worth **€15 total** — thanks to partners
            like MediaMarkt.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits for Guests -->
    <section>
        <h2>A Magical Experience for Every Guest</h2>
        <p>When visitors receive the Magic Safety Sticker, they also receive:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Safety</strong> – knowing help is always close by</li>
            <li><strong>Confidence</strong> – that if they lose something, someone will help</li>
            <li><strong>Joy</strong> – from returning lost items and seeing others smile</li>
            <li><strong>Connection</strong> – through spontaneous, anonymous interactions</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits for Organizers -->
    <section>
        <h2>Why Event Organizers Love It</h2>
        <p>You provide the stickers as part of a branded partnership (e.g., “Gifted by MediaMarkt”) — but the benefits
            keep coming:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Each sticker is linked to your event via a unique discount code (e.g., “EUROPAPARK”)</li>
            <li>Visitors activate their stickers using that code</li>
            <li>After using their free stickers, guests can continue for just <strong>€12/year</strong></li>
            <li>Your event earns a 40% commission when guests upgrade</li>
        </ul>
        <p>It’s a feel-good revenue stream that rewards your guests and boosts your brand reputation.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ol style="padding-left: 1.2rem;">
            <li>Use your event's unique discount code (e.g., “EUROPAPARK”)</li>
            <li>We provide 3 free stickers per guest — a gift worth €15 from partners like MediaMarkt</li>
            <li>Guests activate their stickers using the code at your event</li>
            <li>If they love the experience, they can upgrade to a full year for just €12</li>
            <li>You earn a 40% commission — with zero cost or risk</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <!-- Request Section -->
    <section id="request">
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p>Whether you’re organizing an event or want to promote the Magic Code as an affiliate, we’ve got you covered.
        </p>

        <!-- Tabs -->
        <div class="tabs" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('stickerForm')">Request Free Stickers</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('affiliateForm')">Become an Affiliate</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Sticker Request Form -->
        <div id="stickerForm" class="tab-content" style="display: block;">
            <h3>Request Free Stickers for Your Event</h3>
            <form action="/api/request-stickers" method="POST" enctype="text/plain">
                <label for="sticker-name">Your Name</label><br />
                <input type="text" id="sticker-name" name="name" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="sticker-email">Your Email</label><br />
                <input type="email" id="sticker-email" name="email" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="sticker-event">Event Name</label><br />
                <input type="text" id="sticker-event" name="event" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="sticker-date">Event Date</label><br />
                <input type="date" id="sticker-date" name="event_date" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="sticker-attendees">Expected Attendees</label><br />
                <input type="number" id="sticker-attendees" name="attendees" required class="form-input"><br />

                <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Submit Request</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Affiliate Request Form -->
        <div id="affiliateForm" class="tab-content" style="display: none;">
            <h3>Apply to Become a Magic Code Affiliate</h3>
            <form action="/api/request-affiliate" method="POST" enctype="text/plain">
                <label for="affiliate-name">Full Name</label><br />
                <input type="text" id="affiliate-name" name="name" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="affiliate-email">Email Address</label><br />
                <input type="email" id="affiliate-email" name="email" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="affiliate-platform">Platform or Business Type (e.g., Event Agency, Influencer, Festival
                    Organizer)</label><br />
                <input type="text" id="affiliate-platform" name="platform" required class="form-input"><br />

                <label for="affiliate-experience">Tell us about your experience working with events or
                    communities</label><br />
                <textarea id="affiliate-experience" name="experience" rows="4" required
                    class="form-input"></textarea><br />

                <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Apply Now</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 Magic Code GmbH · All Rights Reserved</p>
        <p>
            <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="#">Terms</a> |
            <a href="#">Contact</a>
        </p>
    </footer>

    <!-- Tab Switching Script -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>

    <script>
        function showTab(tabId) {
            document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(content => content.style.display = 'none');
            document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
            document.getElementById(tabId).style.display = 'block';
            event.currentTarget.classList.add('active');
        }

        document.querySelectorAll('form').forEach(form => {
            form.addEventListener('submit', async function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();

                const formData = new FormData(form);
                const data = Object.fromEntries(formData.entries());

                try {
                    const response = await fetch(form.action, {
                        method: 'POST',
                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                        body: JSON.stringify(data)
                    });

                    const message = await response.text();

                    Swal.fire({
                        icon: 'success',
                        title: 'Submitted!',
                        text: message,
                        confirmButtonColor: '#5898b7'
                    });

                    form.reset();
                } catch (error) {
                    Swal.fire({
                        icon: 'error',
                        title: 'Oops...',
                        text: 'Something went wrong. Please try again later.',
                        confirmButtonColor: '#d33'
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>

</body>

